race.comment: Competitive race but hard to go past PRIDE OF VENUS (3). Won three on end then raced over 1400m for the first time and after spotting a start knuckled down strongly and charged home to just miss. Looks the one to beat. SUPER TALON (8) just missed fresh then disappointed last time. Ideally placed out to 1400m now and worth another chance. VON BEE (1) had been going well and broke through for an overdue win latest. Freshened and has since transferred yards. Has the claim and can measure up this area. AMBERINGER (6) finished seventh last time but only beaten a couple of lengths. Will be winding up late again.
